doc.after: Zinc is included in most single tablet over-the-counter daily vitamin and mineral supplements.[135] Preparations include zinc oxide, zinc acetate, and zinc gluconate.[135] It is believed to possess antioxidant properties, which may protect against accelerated aging of the skin and muscles of the body; studies differ as to its effectiveness.[136] Zinc also helps speed up the healing process after an injury.[136] It is also suspected of being beneficial to the body's immune system. Indeed, zinc deficiency may have effects on virtually all parts of the human immune system.[137]
